import React, { useEffect } from "react"
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles'
import Container from '@material-ui/core/Container'
import Box from '@material-ui/core/Box'
import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid'
import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button'
import Chip from '@material-ui/core/Chip'
import IconButton from '@material-ui/core/IconButton';
import Icon from '@material-ui/core/Icon';
import CloseIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Close';
import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography'
import Avatar from '@material-ui/core/Avatar'
import Divider from '@material-ui/core/Divider'

const useStyles = makeStyles({
  root: {
    position: 'relative',
    display: 'inline-block',
    width: '500px',
    background: "white",
    boxShadow: '0 0 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.25), 0 0 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.22)',
    zIndex:10
  },
  hide: {
    display: "none",
  },
  closeButton: {
   position: 'absolute',
   right: 5,
   top: 5,
   color: "grey",
 },
 image: {
   width: "100px",
   height: "100px"
 },
 topImage: {
   width: "100%",
   height: "200px",
   objectFit: "cover"
 },
});

const Midbar = props => {
  const classes = useStyles()

  return (
    <Box className={props.showMidbar ? classes.root : classes.hide}>

      <Box display="flex" flexDirection="column" alignItems="center">
        <Box mt={4}>
          <Avatar src={'/therapist-images/' + props.therapist.image} className={classes.image}/>
        </Box>

        <Box fontSize="24px" mt={3}>
          {props.therapist.name} {props.therapist.surname}, MSW, LCSW
        </Box>

        <Box color="textSecondary">
          Couples therapist
        </Box>

        <Box pt={2}>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">Email</Button>
          <Button variant="contained" color="secondary">Website</Button>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box px={3}  py={1.5}>
        About {props.therapist.name}
        <Box>
          30 Years of private practice. Masters of Social Work from University of Georigia. Licensed Clinical Social Worker
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box px={3} py={1.5}>
        Specialty Areas
        <Box>
          Depression, Anxiety, Stress, Marriage
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box px={3}  py={1.5}>
        Treatment Approaches
        <Box>
          Emotionally-Focused Therapy, Cognitive Behavioral Therapy
        </Box>
      </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" fontSize="13px" p={3}>
              Do you want help with your life, your work or your relationships? Let’s collaborate to lighten the obstacles to your best life!Do you want help with your life, your work or your relationships? Let’s collaborate to lighten the obstacles to your best life! I offer individual therapy, couples therapy, crisis intervention, pre-marital coaching, family therapy, trauma-informed therapy, personal coaching, and work-life balance coaching. I use best practices that evolve clinically following advances in the research.
            </Box>


            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Experience: 30 Years
            </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Price: $180 per 1 hour session
            </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Education: University of Georigia MSW, LCSW
            </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Treatment Approach: Emotionally Focused Therapy
            </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Specialty Areas: Depression, Anxiety, Marriage
            </Box>

            <Box textAlign="center" mt={3} color="primary">
                Accepts Insurance: No
            </Box>

            <IconButton aria-label="close" className={classes.closeButton} onClick={() => props.setShowMidbar(false)}>
              <CloseIcon />
            </IconButton>


    </Box>
  )

}

export default Midbar
